data.description: Inviting 3 bed/1.5 bath home with a versatile finished shed featuring drywall, electricity, and a covered porch, perfect for a man cave or she-shed. Inside, discover a cozy living area, a kitchen equipped with a stove and dishwasher. Three bedrooms offer comfort and privacy, while the main bathroom offers plenty of storage. Enjoy outdoor gatherings in the spacious backyard. Conveniently located near amenities, this home offers functional living space. Call today to set up your showing.
